    "bio": "👋 Hi, I’m SuS\n.\nI build custom n8n workflows, automations & AI integrations to help businesses save time and scale smarter.\n\nI share templates, answer questions and love exploring creative use cases – from lead generation to data workflows and AI-powered automations. 🚀\n\nAlways happy to connect, learn and contribute to the community.\n\nAlthough my profile is in English, I am a native German speaker and happy to work in both German and English projects.",
